      <title>南非非洲人国民大会因祖马组建敌对政党将其驱逐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/south-africa-s-anc-expels-zuma-over-formation-of-rival-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非非洲人国民大会开除了前领导人雅各布·祖马，原因是他成立了竞争政治团体，导致该党自三十年前执政以来首次失去议会多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/south-africa-s-anc-expels-zuma-over-formation-of-rival-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯亿万富翁遗产被没收数千美元，以结束英国制裁案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/russian-petr-aven-s-estate-forfeits-thousands-to-end-uk-sanctions-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯亿万富翁彼得·阿文 (Petr Aven) 的遗产经理同意放弃超过 75 万英镑（963,260 美元），以结束英国警方对逃避制裁的近两年调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/russian-petr-aven-s-estate-forfeits-thousands-to-end-uk-sanctions-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:58:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚全国生活成本抗议活动爆发前燃料短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/nigeria-fuel-runs-short-before-national-cost-of-living-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚全国范围内的示威活动定于周四开始，抗议该国的生活成本危机，而示威活动即将到来，尼日利亚面临着燃料短缺的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/nigeria-fuel-runs-short-before-national-cost-of-living-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:54:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼发挥调解人作用平衡中欧关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/meloni-tells-xi-italy-can-broker-balanced-ties-between-eu-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼提出要促进中国与欧盟之间改善贸易关系，并呼吁习近平主席“平衡”欧盟与世界第二大经济体之间的贸易关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/meloni-tells-xi-italy-can-broker-balanced-ties-between-eu-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选前中国抓住机会在乌克兰扮演和平使者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-seizes-chance-to-play-peacemaker-in-ukraine-before-us-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国和欧洲对北京支持克里姆林宫的战场行动的批评日益增多，国家主席习近平仍在加紧努力，将自己定位为结束俄罗斯在乌克兰战争的和平使者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-seizes-chance-to-play-peacemaker-in-ukraine-before-us-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈兰袭击事件发生后，德国敦促其公民离开黎巴嫩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/germany-urges-its-citizens-to-leave-lebanon-after-golan-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列指责真主党对戈兰高地数名儿童遇难的袭击事件负责，局势愈发紧张，德国呼吁其在黎巴嫩的公民紧急离开该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/germany-urges-its-citizens-to-leave-lebanon-after-golan-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:37:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯瓦格纳部队遭遇部署马里以来最大伤亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/russia-s-wagner-suffers-most-casualties-since-deploying-to-mali</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据亲克里姆林宫的新闻消息来源称，上周，俄罗斯瓦格纳集团的二十多名雇佣兵和马里士兵在与马里北部叛军作战时丧生，这可能是该组织自 2021 年部署到这个西非国家以来最大的死亡人数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/russia-s-wagner-suffers-most-casualties-since-deploying-to-mali</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:19:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
